<p><strong>They Thought Loved Ones Were Calling for Help:</strong> It Was an AI Scam: We address the ethical implications of AI-powered scams, where human vulnerabilities are exploited through advanced AI-generated content. We examine the potential consequences on trust, emotional well-being, and the need for robust safeguards in AI systems.</p>
